    211  f065							; Reseed the PRNG from the free-running frame counter (mixed with whatever
    212  f065							; state carried over), so each restart differs -- the human-variable delay
    213  f065							; before pressing fire makes frameCnt effectively random. Keep it non-zero
    214  f065							; (an all-zero LFSR is a dead state).
