    222  f06f							; Start with EMPTY platforms: every entity begins hidden and slides in from
    223  f06f							; the right edge on a staggered delay (via the normal respawn path, which
    224  f06f							; rolls a random type and clears gaps). This guarantees reaction time on any
    225  f06f							; floor the player jumps to -- nothing is ever sitting in the jump path at
    226  f06f							; the fixed player x. entX is set when each one spawns; entDrawLo = blank.
