   1048  f4ca							;   Each entry strobes RESM0; the $1C (NOP abs) swallows the next
   1049  f4ca							;   entry's `sta RESM0`, so only the jumped-to strobe executes, then
   1050  f4ca							;   execution falls through to `sta HMOVE` at cycle ~74.
